{"type":null,"faqId":33939,"title":"语音唤醒怎么使用？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:11pt;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.s2{font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>语音唤醒默认是关闭的，请在设置-智能辅助-语音唤醒下，开启语音唤醒开关。进行简单的设置和语音训练后，就可以使用语音唤醒功能了。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>目前，例如荣耀7的语音唤醒主要支持两类功能：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1）语音找手机，您可以说“荣耀，小7，你在哪儿”</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2）语音打电话，您可以说“荣耀，小7，打电话给小华”</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">提醒：</span><span class=\"s2\"> 如果只说“荣耀，小7”的话，只会亮起屏幕，并不会有提示音； 只有再说“你在哪儿”或“打电话给XXX”时，才会有提示音和进一步的动作；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=108636\" style=\"width:2.242361in;height:3.9868054in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=108637\" style=\"width:2.2416666in;height:3.9895833in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=108638\" style=\"width:2.2222223in;height:3.9534721in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=108639\" style=\"width:2.2222223in;height:3.9534721in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8641","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748765000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":61,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"语音唤醒,使用","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}